Package: harper
Type: Package
Title: Harmonic Regression and Periodicity Test
Version: 1.0-2
Date: 2018-03-18
Author: Yuanhao Lai and A.I. McLeod
Maintainer: Yuanhao Lai <ylai72@uwo.ca>
Depends: R (>= 3.0),
Description: Implements p-value computations using an approximation to the cumulative distribution function for a variety of tests for periodicity. Fits four parameter harmonic regression using LS, L1 and robust regression and the semiparametric harmonic regression using the single index model with monotonic constraint. An accompanying vignette illustrates the application of these tests and models.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: yes
Imports: quantreg (>= 5.0),robustbase, MASS, scam, mgcv, scar,Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Suggests: knitr, boot, lattice, rmarkdown, GeneCycle, stabledist,
        ggplot2, tidyverse
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LinkingTo: Rcpp
URL: https://github.com/CliffordLai/harper
BugReports: https://github.com/CliffordLai/harper/issues
Packaged: 2018-03-19 04:57:54 UTC; Yi
